      • getSTAFLogDirectory

        protected java.lang.String getSTAFLogDirectory()
        Description copied from class: STAFFileLogItem
        Returns the DIRECTORY setting of the STAF LOG service. This method is defined as abstract. Because STAF 2 and STAF 3 return unmarshalled and marshalled result. While to unmarshall the result, we must import the STAF 3 library; To separate STAF 2 and STAF 3, this method is defined as abstract, and it will be implemented in STAFTextLogItem, STAFTextLogItem3, STAFXmlLogItem and STAFXmlLogItem3.

        Specified by:
        getSTAFLogDirectory in class STAFFileLogItem
        Returns:
        the Directory setting as returned by LIST SETTINGS request to STAF LOG service.
